== Ruth achem Pustok ==
'''Book of Ruth'''

[[File:Julius Schnorr von Carolsfeld- Ruth im Feld des Boaz.jpg|thumb|Ruth, Boaz-achea Xetant]]


Ruthachem Pustok ekdom’lhan.  Hea Pustokant ruth nanvache eke ostorechi kotha vornnilea.

Ruth hi Moabit ostori.  Ti eka Israelit mon’xa lagim logn zaloli.  To melea uprant ti Naomi aple sasumaim-xim ravunk Judant portoto.  Hanga ti, Boaz hea tichea ghovachea soirea lagim logn zata.  Hea logna vorvim tika Obed zolmota.  Obed zaun asa Davidacho xapai.

Hi ek dekhivont kotha.  Eke videxi ostoren porian Devacher aplo visvas dovorlo zalear,  Dev apli konnvallai dakhoita tem ruthachea Pustokant bhes bore torem dakhoilam.

Ruthachea pustokak kherit mol ieta kiteak adim thaun Ruth Davidachi vhoddli xamai koxi porompora manun gheit ailea, ani Matev Xubhvortoman’kar Jezu Kristachi conxavoll ditana,  Ruthachem nanv gheta.  Polle Mt. 1/5



